{"tid":1485744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係勸都俾啲禮貌唔好下下又割又鬼好唔好？","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:56:13.000Z","uid":189277,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f256900ea5d9818db1b8495fed89ac9c182573","tid":1485744,"uid":189277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>其實前線手足有幾何得閒碌手機</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係發晦氣，但要勸，就真係自己落場勸<br />\n<br />\n上過前線就知，其實邊到得閒碌連登，係都睇咗telegram睇下消息先啦<br />\n<br />\n一返到去上到嚟，又弱智，又割，又公安，又鬼，真係會睇到燥，睇到低落<br />\n<br />\n其實前線等後面走，後面等前線走，係現場都可以等好耐架，又唔似得我地係屋企涼冷氣睇新聞知哂咩事<br />\n<br />\n係唔割就真係唔割，好言相勸，係勸就落場勸，唔好屌人老母又話人係鬼跟住補句唔割就算<br />\n<br />\n真真正正不割蓆好唔好？"},{"pid":"81e47312fac4f42f1bdc95c8680f79aeb7a32ac6","tid":1485744,"uid":189277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:34:52.000Z","msg":"不割蓆！"},{"pid":"0fe6c27873bf7cad342964fc6a94227dfdb01c27","tid":1485744,"uid":189277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"咩叫核彈都唔割？"},{"pid":"6436a8f03e542057348856f261cccedfd48fa7c8","tid":1485744,"uid":189277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:21.000Z","msg":"咩叫錫春袋都唔割？"},{"pid":"1ed83ee4fd8f40ee4ec814373fbd84f987023fbd","tid":1485744,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f815baaf9b5d064cdc88a79bbcbe97d1b0a1c0","tid":1485744,"uid":189277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"唔割呀！"},{"pid":"01b5c972733554c55b2f64ae0d6991e0d1c10473","tid":1485744,"uid":26298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6f256900ea5d9818db1b8495fed89ac9c182573","tid":1485744,"uid":189277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color